      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new streetwear collection for my brand and i really want to make sure we're being respectful. i don't want the designs to feel like cultural appropriation or like we're just \"playing dress up\" with something we don't understand. can you help me define what the \"authentic\" aesthetic of urban culture actually looks like so i can stay on the right side of that line?",
